        <main class="container" style="padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 5rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>

            <div class="prose" style="line-height: 1.6; color: #4B5563;">
                <p class="mb-4">Welcome to Zen Tea. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your
                    personal data. This brief privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your
                    information.</p>

                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-6 mb-2 text-gray-900">1. Information We Collect</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">When you register an account, place an order, or interact with our services, we may
                    collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, delivery address, and
                    payment details.</p>

                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-6 mb-2 text-gray-900">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                <p class="mb-2">We use the information we collect solely to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
                    <li>Process, track, and fulfill your beverage orders.</li>
                    <li>Manage your account and shopping cart preferences.</li>
                    <li>Communicate with you regarding order updates or customer support.</li>
                    <li>Improve our system and user experience.</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-6 mb-2 text-gray-900">3. Data Protection and Sharing</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">We implement standard security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized
                    access. We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We only share
                    necessary details with trusted partners (such as payment gateways or delivery services) strictly for
                    the purpose of fulfilling your order.</p>

                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-6 mb-2 text-gray-900">4. Cookies</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">Our website uses cookies to keep you logged in, remember your cart items, and provide a
                    seamless browsing experience.</p>

                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-6 mb-2 text-gray-900">5. Contact Us</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, please
                    contact us at zentea@email.com.my.</p>
            </div>
        </main>

